history.content: You should go on decal.org, and you can look at all the Decals being offered for that semester. This website tells you how to enroll in each decal, since many decals have their own enrollment processes. Also the iosdecal when I took it required submitting an application.

children.subject: Also note that many of these decals don't open enrollment until much later (i.e., the first couple weeks of the semester) which can be annoying, but keep your eyes open! Btw the iOS decal is pretty awesome, you will learn a lot!
